<L>__{exterior d.e.f. day}
<A>__{from a distance, schindler can be seen arguing with an ss officer who's trying to hand him papers, orders of some kind, which the irate industrialist refuses to accept. here, closer, carrying blankets and bundles, schindler's workers are marched under heavy guard out of the factory and its annexes and across the fortified yard. his people are being taken. where, is unclear. schindler abruptly breaks off the discussion with the ss man, climbs into his car and drives off.}
